e, not missing setup.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"No environment or system property setup is indicated. If tests exercise WebAppClassLoader directly, update the test code for Jetty 9.4.0.RC1: Context now uses isSystemClass(Class<?>) and isServerClass(Class<?>) and also requires isServerResource(String, URL) and isSystemResource(String, URL). Prefer constructing a real WebAppContext with a temporary WEB-INF/web.xml/static webapp for coverage where possible.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"jetty-jmx is an optional dependency and should only be added if tests intentionally cover JMX behavior.\",\n    \"Jetty distribution/demo-base style tests may require jetty.home/jetty.base, but embedded WebAppContext coverage does not.\",\n    \"Local Gradle and native-image verification remain authoritative for any old-Jetty-on-JDK-25 runtime issues.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0252e8480e19a0c6016a425a6386748196aad485aa1850d208\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2737, "output": 1026, "cacheRead": 19968, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23731, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782733398419, "responseId": "resp_0252e8480e19a0c6016a425a56dd188196923cabcccccf35b5"}, "toolResults": []}
